title: Simone Biles Rising | Part 2 Official Trailer | Netflix
description:
Victory begins within. Four years since Simone Biles had to pull out of the 2020 Olympics, witness the thrilling conclusion of the road to glory and her ultimate comeback. See the tears, the perseverance, and the moments behind her status as one of the greatest athletes of all time and cementing her incredible legacy at the 2024 Paris Olympics.

Watch Simone Biles Rising Pt 2, only on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/simonebiles
